title: slow wave of the `wedge` of two tremoloing samples
pid: c38f063a-7793-46ec-a030-c8efcd4a1cff
body: |2-
  #+BEGIN_SRC haskell
    d1 $ wedge
      ( -- The fraction can itself be a signal
        slow 16 $ tri + 0.2 )
      (fast 16 $ s "lt")
      (fast 16 $ rev (s "cp") |*| amp 0.2)
  #+END_SRC
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
